NameofManga: Hanging Out With A Gamer Girl
Author: Niichi,
Description: Terazaki Kaoru is about to meet up with his online friend, Nanami. But Nanami doesn't know Terazaki is a guy in real life! He's sure to be disappointed and at least a little weirded out. But Terazaki is in for a surprise...
AlternativeNames: Real mo Tamaniwa wo Tsuku,Gemuzuki no Tomodachi to Iroiro suru Hanashi,Sometimes Reality Tells Lies, Too,現実もたまには嘘をつく,ゲーム好きの友達と色々する話
